title: Bill dissolving Wisconsin elections board advances
text: MADISON, Wis. (AP) - Democrats argued Thursday they were being bullied by Republicans but were unable to stop a fast-tracked bill doing away with Wisconsin's unique nonpartisan elections board from moving one step closer to passage.
